title: Ep. - 375 - BIG BROTHER WITH ROB CESTERNINO CARLOS KING, EXECUTIVE PRODUCER OF BET PRESENTS: THE ENCORE
description:
Rob Cesternino from Rob Has a Podcast and the go-to expert on all things Big Brother reviews season 23 of the CBS hit, which features a group of people living together in a large house, isolated from the outside world but continuously watched by television cameras.

 

Carlos King is the Executive Producer of BET Presents: The Encore, which chronicles 9 former R&B girl-group members & recording artists as they form a supergroup to create an album within 30 days.

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
